Tiffany - Radikal Redz Shopping with Tiffany || 11-18-2023 (1pm-3pm)
160 Broadway Ave, Bartow, FL, United States, Florida
This unique opportunity with Tiffany as part of her Radikal Redz showcase includes a shopping experience for one-of a kind stage-worn outfits & accessories as well as hand-painted jackets (denim and others).   There will be a 10% coupon provided at the door & a drawing for a $25 coupon/bundle surprise for all ticketed attendees.
This is not a performance, there are separate tickets for that event later today at Unfiltered-Lakeland
Limited to 50 attendees, RSVP required
For RSVP and information, visit; Brown Paper Tickets and search “Tiffany” or Event # 6122296
… or follow the link below:
